#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.cos.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.cos"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.cos.cos:1 of
msgid "Cosine element-wise."
msgstr "逐元素计算余弦值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.cos.cos of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.cos.cos:3 of
msgid "Input tensor in radians."
msgstr "以弧度为单位的输入张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.cos.cos:5 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated array is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供，其形状必须可以广播到输入。如果未提供或为 `"
"None`，则返回一个新分配的数组。元组（只能作为关键字参数）的长度必须等于"
"输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.cos.cos:10 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "值为 True 表示在该位置计算 ufunc，值为 False 表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.cos.cos of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.cos.cos:15 of
msgid "**y** -- The corresponding cosine values."
msgstr "**y** -- 对应的余弦值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.cos.cos of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.cos.cos:19 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.cos.cos:20 of
msgid ""
"If `out` is provided, the function writes the result into it, and returns"
" a reference to `out`.  (See Examples)"
msgstr ""
"如果提供了 `out`，函数会将结果写入其中，并返回对 `out` 的引用。（参见示例"
"）"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.cos.cos:24 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.cos.cos:25 of
msgid ""
"M. Abramowitz and I. A. Stegun, Handbook of Mathematical Functions. New "
"York, NY: Dover, 1972."
msgstr "M. Abramowitz 和 I. A. Stegun，《数学函数手册》，纽约：Dover，1972年。"

